#Question 9
#Explain how the "+", addition operation works differently for integers and strings

#Integer addition
apple = 1
orange = 3
print(apple + orange)
#output = 4

#String addition
apple = str(apple)
orange = str(orange)
print(apple+orange)
#output = 13

